Class SieveUI

java.lang.Object
  SieveUI

public class SieveUI
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the user interface for the Sieve program. It will get a valid value from the user and print out a list of all the prime numbers up to that value. It will also print out the percentage of prime numbers. The program will continue to prompt the user for another value until the user stops the program with the exit code.
